{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_4605c0e8-c9ec-4645-a3cf-345e5bb6d67","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/02-角色库与人设编辑.md"},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 角色库与人设编辑（代码事实）\n\n> 对照：`apps/studioV2` 角色页 + 故事编辑器角色 FormModal。  \n> 产品字段意图见 [需求 11](../../AI和人类/需求/11-角色与社交.md)。  \n> 固化：2026-07-22（V2-T3-8：角色/编辑器锚点均磁盘 + API；`MOCK_EDITOR_CHARACTERS` 已删）。\n\n## 1. 磁盘五人真源（已接通）\n\n真源：`data/characters/*.json` ↔ Next `/api/characters`（ajaxProxy：`library/api/charactersApi.ts`）。  \n**已删除：** `MOCK_CHARACTERS` / `mockCharactersData.ts` / `listMockCharacters` / `commitUpdateCharacterMock` 等角色业务 mock 入口（无兼容壳）。\n\n| agentId | 显示名 | personalityCode | 备注 |\n|---------|--------|-----------------|------|\n| `lanxing` | 澜星姐姐 | ENFJ | 电话 2267070 |\n| `xiaopi` | 小皮 | ENFP | |\n| `qiang-shushu` | 强叔叔 | ESTP | |\n| `zhang-boss` | 张老板 | INTJ | |\n| `bai-bansian` | 白半仙 | INFJ | 号码 010 |\n\n- **来源意图：** doubaoSister 正式角色设定稿「错误电话之前」必要 5 人。  \n- **落盘：** 正式五人 JSON 在 `data/characters/`；库页列表经 `fetchCharacterDefs()` → **走** `/api/characters`。  \n- **增删改：** `commitCreateCharacter` / `commitDeleteCharacter` / `commitSaveCharacterDetail` 写盘后刷新可见。\n\n## 2. 投影与表单贯通\n\n```text\nCharacterSummary (typeFiles/.../characterSummary.ts)\n  ↔ toCharacterDetailFormValues / applyCharacterDetailForm\n  ↔ CharacterDetailFormValues (Formik)\n  ↔ characterDefToSummary / mergeDetailFormIntoCharacterDef  (落盘 CharacterDef)\n```\n\n关键文件：\n\n- Items：`bis/.../characterDetailFormItems.ts`  \n  - 基本信息：`CHARACTER_BASIC_ITEMS`（含音色 Select）  \n  - 提示词：`CHARACTER_PROMPT_ITEMS`（含 **人格类型** `persona.personalityCode`）  \n- 校验：展示字段编辑态**全必填**（含 personalityCode）。  \n- MBTI 选项：`typeFiles/library/characters/persona/personalityCodeOptions.ts`（16 型）。  \n- 音色选项：`typeFiles/library/characters/realtime/realtimeVoiceOptions.ts`（引擎只存 `voiceId` 字符串）。\n\n## 3. 哪里能编角色\n\n| 入口 | 行为 |\n|------|------|\n| 角色库详情页 | `CharacterDetailEditForm` + BASIC/PROMPT items；保存走 API |\n| 故事编辑器选中锚点 | `StoryEditorCharacterModals` 复用同一套 items；打开前 `fetchCharacterDef` |\n| 画布「添加角色」 | 先走精简 `CREATE_CHARACTER_*` → `commitCreateCharacter`，再可编辑详情槽 |\n\n画布角色锚点 **打开时**由 `bundle.participants` + `/api/characters` 的 displayName 生成（`diskBundleGraph`）；`pendingCardCount` 由当前包内卡归属统计。**不是**独立 mock 数组；完整人设仍按 agentId 从 API 取。\n\n## 4. persona.personalityCode 业务理解\n\n- Studio：Select 写入投影字段；保存时 trim 后进 CharacterDef。  \n- 引擎：见 [05-引擎Composer与personalityCode.md](./05-引擎Composer与personalityCode.md)。  \n- UI helperText 已写明会进 Composer systemHard（演示口径；Host 真跑另议）。\n\n## 5. 已知小不一致（勿当 bug 乱修扩大范围）\n\n- 部分磁盘 `voiceId`（如 `zh_child_boy`、`zh_male_elder`）**不在** `REALTIME_VOICE_OPTIONS` 枚举内；下拉可能显示空/异常，属音色枚举未扩全，与 MBTI 任务无关。  \n- `createEmptyCharacterDetailSlots` 默认 personalityCode = 选项表第一项（ISTJ），新建后再改。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":62,"fileSize":3445,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/02-角色库与人设编辑.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":62},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_4605c0e8-c9ec-4645-a3cf-345e5bb6d67","startedAtMs":"1784713133681","completedAtMs":"1784713133933"},"model_call_id":"02362126-05ae-43d8-abe9-d65b44749433-2-zoky","session_id":"61591ea5-b391-41b5-8eac-a8cd307c2c21","timestamp_ms":1784713133744}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_1d6bf836-72dd-4219-a98b-98c800f7c08","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/04-第一幕打错电话-mock拓扑.md"},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 第一幕《打错电话》· 磁盘包拓扑（代码事实）\n\n> 正式稿（仓外）：`doubaoSister/.../定稿的故事/1.第一幕初识.md`（标题《打错电话》）。  \n> **运行时真源：** `data/storis-packages/wrong_number_act1/`（`story.conf.json` + `cards/*.s-card.json` + `canvas.layout.json`）。  \n> **编辑器投影：** `bis/pageBis/storyEditor/package/graph/diskBundleGraph.ts`（`bundleToEditorGraph` / `editorGraphToBundle`）。  \n> 固化：2026-07-22（V2-T3-8）；文件名保留「mock拓扑」仅为历史导航，**不再指 CanvasMockGraph**。\n\n## 1. 包 / 章节展示名\n\n| 键 | 当前值 | 说明 |\n|----|--------|------|\n| `packageId` | `wrong_number_act1` | 正式语义 id；与 `story.conf.json` 一致 |\n| 列表 title | `第一幕：打错电话` | 磁盘 `story.conf.json` |\n| chapter_start.title | `第一幕 · 打错电话` | `canvas.layout.json` |\n| entryCardId | `lanxing_wrong_number` | `story.conf.json` |\n| participants | `lanxing` · `xiaopi` | conf + layout lanes |\n\n## 2. 卡拓扑（业务理解）\n\n磁盘 cardId 与画布 nodeId 映射见 layout；叙事结构：\n\n```text\nchapter_start\n    → lanxing_wrong_number「打错电话」(lanxing, outbound_auto)\n         exit_callback「挂机后补打」\n           effects: attach_call_card → lanxing_callback_intro\n                    schedule_call_card delayMinutes=2\n           story 边 + attach 效果边 → lanxing_callback_intro\n    → lanxing_callback_intro「补打自报」\n         exit_known「记住名号」→ end_story → chapter_end\n         exit_voicemail「没说清→留言」→ create_voicemail → lanxing_voicemail\n    → lanxing_voicemail「语音留言」→ end_story → chapter_end\nchapter_end.summary：小皮收拾书包 / 纸条 / 拿起电话（下章钩子，无独立小皮卡）\n```\n\n三张叙事卡 **均归属澜星**；左侧角色锚点来自 participants + 角色库 displayName。\n\n## 3. 与正式稿节拍对照\n\n| 正式稿节拍 | 磁盘落点 | 偏差备注 |\n|------------|----------|----------|\n| 第一次误拨、闲聊、不留名号挂断 | `lanxing_wrong_number` | speakable 为压缩台词，非逐句剧本 |\n| 补打自报、问称呼、留 2267070、提小皮露营 | `lanxing_callback_intro` | 「告诉名字 / 不告诉」收敛成两条出口 |\n| 未说清 → 语音信箱 | `create_voicemail` + `lanxing_voicemail` | 留言 effect + 可读卡 |\n| 文末小皮 vignette | `chapter_end.summary` | **刻意**不做小皮 CallCard |\n| 「没过多久再响」 | `schedule_call_card` 2 分钟 | UI 投影；Host 未跑 |\n\n## 4. 历史：从会话 mock 迁到磁盘\n\n已删除的打开/列表 mock 路径：\n\n- `CanvasMockGraph.ts` / `.edges.ts`（内存唯一种子）  \n- `MOCK_STORY_PACKAGES` 作列表或打开真源  \n- 旧 packageId `pkg_memory_bar_1` 作正式第一幕包（现仅调试器/设置展示 mock 可能引用）\n\n替换原因：第三步要求真实业务接线；打开只读磁盘，保存整包写回。\n\n## 5. 角色锚点计数\n\n打开包时 `diskBundleGraph` 按各卡 `ownerAgentId` 统计 `pendingCardCount`；澜星通常为 3，小皮 0（文末镜头），其余参与者 0。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":61,"fileSize":3189,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/04-第一幕打错电话-mock拓扑.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":61},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_1d6bf836-72dd-4219-a98b-98c800f7c08","startedAtMs":"1784713133684","completedAtMs":"1784713133936"},"model_call_id":"02362126-05ae-43d8-abe9-d65b44749433-2-zoky","session_id":"61591ea5-b391-41b5-8eac-a8cd307c2c21","timestamp_ms":1784713133747}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_6b5273f6-8903-4256-b1cf-a7eff6b1564","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/library/api/charactersApi.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 角色库 BFF 请求：读写 data/characters（经 /api/characters）。\n\t* 仅返回 CharacterDef 形状；投影到 CharacterSummary 在 bis。\n\t*/\nimport type { CharacterDef } from \"@airpc/rpg-engine\";\nimport { parseStudioApiJson } from \"@studio-v2/src/utils/ajaxHelper/studioApiClient\";\n\nexport type CharactersListData = {\n\tcharacters: CharacterDef[];\n};\n\nexport type CharacterOneData = {\n\tcharacter: CharacterDef;\n};\n\n/** GET /api/characters：列出磁盘角色 */\nexport async function fetchCharacterDefs(): Promise<CharacterDef[]> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(\"/api/characters\");\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<CharactersListData>(res);\n\treturn data.characters;\n}\n\n/** GET /api/characters/:agentId */\nexport async function fetchCharacterDef(\n\tagentId: string,\n): Promise<CharacterDef> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/characters/${encodeURIComponent(agentId)}`);\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<CharacterOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.character;\n}\n\n/** PUT /api/characters/:agentId：整卡落盘 */\nexport async function putCharacterDef(\n\tagentId: string,\n\tcharacter: CharacterDef,\n): Promise<CharacterDef> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/characters/${encodeURIComponent(agentId)}`, {\n\t\tmethod: \"PUT\",\n\t\theaders: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\" },\n\t\tbody: JSON.stringify({ character }),\n\t});\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<CharacterOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.character;\n}\n\n/** POST /api/characters：新建落盘 */\nexport async function postCharacterDef(\n\tcharacter: CharacterDef,\n): Promise<CharacterDef> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(\"/api/characters\", {\n\t\tmethod: \"POST\",\n\t\theaders: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\" },\n\t\tbody: JSON.stringify({ character }),\n\t});\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<CharacterOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.character;\n}\n\n/** DELETE /api/characters/:agentId */\nexport async function deleteCharacterDef(agentId: string): Promise<void> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/characters/${encodeURIComponent(agentId)}`, {\n\t\tmethod: \"DELETE\",\n\t});\n\tawait parseStudioApiJson<{ ok: true }>(res);\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":66,"fileSize":2064,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/library/api/charactersApi.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":66},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_6b5273f6-8903-4256-b1cf-a7eff6b1564","startedAtMs":"1784713133690","completedAtMs":"1784713133936"},"model_call_id":"02362126-05ae-43d8-abe9-d65b44749433-2-zoky","session_id":"61591ea5-b391-41b5-8eac-a8cd307c2c21","timestamp_ms":1784713133749}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_df9635be-a846-4b52-8228-667db792d23","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/library/api/usersApi.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 玩家配置 BFF：读写 data/users/<userId>/profile.save.json 的 user 段。\n\t* 记忆区仍用摘要字段；列表与详情用完整 User。\n\t*/\nimport type { User } from \"@airpc/rpg-engine\";\nimport { parseStudioApiJson } from \"@studio-v2/src/utils/ajaxHelper/studioApiClient\";\nimport type { DiskUserSummaryDto } from \"@studio-v2/typeFiles/library/users/diskUserSummary\";\n\nexport type UsersListData = {\n\tusers: User[];\n};\n\nexport type UserOneData = {\n\tuser: User;\n};\n\n/**\n\t* GET /api/users — 磁盘各 Profile 的 user 段列表。\n\t*/\nexport async function fetchProfileUsers(): Promise<User[]> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(\"/api/users\");\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<UsersListData>(res);\n\treturn data.users;\n}\n\n/**\n\t* GET /api/users — 投影为记忆区调试 userId 下拉摘要。\n\t*/\nexport async function fetchDiskUserSummaries(): Promise<DiskUserSummaryDto[]> {\n\tconst users = await fetchProfileUsers();\n\treturn users.map(function (u) {\n\t\treturn {\n\t\t\tuserId: u.userId,\n\t\t\tnickname: u.nickname,\n\t\t\tcreatedAt: u.createdAt,\n\t\t};\n\t});\n}\n\n/** GET /api/users/:userId — 回读单用户 user 段 */\nexport async function fetchProfileUser(userId: string): Promise<User> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/users/${encodeURIComponent(userId)}`);\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<UserOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.user;\n}\n\n/** POST /api/users — 新建薄 Profile 并写 user 段 */\nexport async function postProfileUser(user: User): Promise<User> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(\"/api/users\", {\n\t\tmethod: \"POST\",\n\t\theaders: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\" },\n\t\tbody: JSON.stringify({ user }),\n\t});\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<UserOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.user;\n}\n\n/**\n\t* PUT /api/users/:userId — 仅更新 user 段；响应为写后回读。\n\t*/\nexport async function putProfileUser(\n\tuserId: string,\n\tuser: User,\n): Promise<User> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/users/${encodeURIComponent(userId)}`, {\n\t\tmethod: \"PUT\",\n\t\theaders: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\" },\n\t\tbody: JSON.stringify({ user }),\n\t});\n\tconst data = await parseStudioApiJson<UserOneData>(res);\n\treturn data.user;\n}\n\n/** DELETE /api/users/:userId */\nexport async function deleteProfileUser(userId: string): Promise<void> {\n\tconst res = await fetch(`/api/users/${encodeURIComponent(userId)}`, {\n\t\tmethod: \"DELETE\",\n\t});\n\tawait parseStudioApiJson<{ ok: true }>(res);\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":81,"fileSize":2381,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/library/api/usersApi.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":81},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_df9635be-a846-4b52-8228-667db792d23","startedAtMs":"1784713133693","completedAtMs":"1784713133939"},"model_call_id":"02362126-05ae-43d8-abe9-d65b44749433-2-zoky","session_id":"61591ea5-b391-41b5-8eac-a8cd307c2c21","timestamp_ms":1784713133754}
